data.description: Your new backyard Oasis is awaiting you in Walton Creek! This beautiful newly constructed home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a loft.  Enjoy watching the sunrise with a cup of coffee on the front porch or relax and unwind during the evening outside in the private fenced-in and lighted backyard with lots of beautiful natural pines and shrubbery.  Under the extra-large back patio, soak in the huge 6 person hot tub.  Paired with your favorite Google or Alexa device this home can be used as a smart home and let technology do all the work for you!  The garage door, thermostats, inside lights, front and back outdoor lights, and security system can all be given commands to operate for you while you relax and enjoy!
